description: Minisforum has recently announced the pre-sale of a new Mini-PC, which is built around the latest generation AMD Ryzen 9 8945HS processor, featuring the advanced Zen 4 architecture. This device supports DDR5 dual-channel memory and utilizes M.2 2280 slots for SSD storage. The Minisforum UM890 Pro is equipped with the AMD Ryzen 9 8945HS processor […]
title: Minisforum UM890 Pro Taps AMD Ryzen 9 8945HS Processor
